      "details": "\n            \n        <div class=\"card-detail-body\">\n            <div class=\"row hmr-6\">\n                <div class=\"col-12 mt-2\">\n                    <h2 class=\"jobtitle mb-1 pb-1\">Talent Scout  Mooinooi</h2>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"row\">\n                <div class=\"col\">\n                    <h2 class=\"opportunity-company mb-1 pb-1\">Zibuke Africa</h2>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n                <div class=\"row verified mb-3 mt-0\">\n                    <div class=\"col\">\n                        <p class=\"verified-text\"><i class=\"icon icon-check2-circle\" style=\"margin-right:2px;\"></i><span>Partner Opportunity</span></p>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            <div class=\"row\">\n                <div class=\"col\">\n                    <div class=\"card-detail-meta mt-0\">\n                            <div class=\"meta-item\">\n                                <i class=\"icon icon-geo-pin-solid\"></i>\n                                <p class=\"mb-0\"><strong>Location: </strong>Mooinooi, North West</p>\n                            </div>\n\n                            <div class=\"meta-item\">\n                                <i class=\"icon icon-calendar-event-solid\"></i>\n                                <p class=\"mb-0\"><strong>Date posted:</strong> 23 February 2024</p>\n                            </div>\n                            <div class=\"meta-item\">\n                                <i class=\"icon icon-calendar-x\"></i>\n                                <p class=\"mb-0\"><strong>Closing date:</strong> 22 March 2024 </p>\n                            </div>\n                            <div class=\"meta-item\">\n                                <i class=\"icon icon-briefcase\"></i>\n                                <p class=\"mb-0\"><strong>Job type: </strong>Fixed-term</p>\n                            </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"row\">\n                <div class=\"col\">\n                    <h6 class=\"opportunity-reference mb-3 mt-3\">Reference number: 1356210</h6>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"card-detail-body\">\n            <div class=\"row\">\n                <div class=\"col text-break\">\n                            <h2>Role description</h2>\n                            <p class=\"text-break white-space-pre-line\"></p><p><strong>Zibuke Africa</strong> is a company that uses live competitions to find talented individuals that can:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Sing.</li>\n<li>Dance.</li>\n<li>Produce art work.</li>\n<li>Tell stories that depict African culture and heritage.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>We call these people Keepers. We then pay them to perform in our weekend culture and heritage festivals. We also offer subsidized training and practice in:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Videography.</li>\n<li>Playing indigenous music instruments.</li>\n<li>Acting.</li>\n<li>Movie directing.</li>\n<li>Script writing.</li>\n<li>Art work creation.</li>\n<li>Book writing.</li>\n<li>Mobile game development.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Graduates are then hired to produce content for the company. We make money from corporate sponsorship and subscriptions.</p><p></p>\n                            <h2>Role requirement</h2>\n                            <p class=\"text-break white-space-pre-line\"></p><p>Should you be employed you will work to organise live culture and heritage competitions in townships and villages around South Africa.</p>\n<p><strong>KEY QUALITIES.</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>You should be a self-start that can work without supervision.</li>\n<li>Be a problem solver.</li>\n<li>Be someone who seeks opportunities that allow them to learn and grow their skills.</li>\n<li>Enjoy taking opportunities that challenge and reward you based on the results you produce.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>&nbsp;</p><p></p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n            <hr>\n                                \n        </div>\n    ",
